map-integration/map-component.html.body:
MapComponent
Wrapper for an OpenLayers map. The ol.map is passed to the MapComponent as a prop.


The map object can be shared across the whole application without passing it as prop to the whole render tree.
The map can be created asynchronusly (using a Promise) so that every child of the MapProvider is just rendered when the map is ready.

Documentation


